  "validation_notes": "--project-transport-plan, --segment-start, and --segment-end are required. status must be one of editing, pending, active and is required server-side. confirm-at-max must be RFC3339 when provided. If status is active, a driver must be assigned. segment-start and segment-end must belong to the same project transport plan, and segment-start position must be <= segment-end position. When a driver is present, all segments in range must have a trucker, the driver must have membership with each trucker in the range, and the driver cannot overlap existing assignments for the same plan. Inbound project offices must belong to the same broker as the project."
